Archivista Perl Class Library
=============================

o Installation
--------------

Copy the Archivista.pm Module and the Archivista directory to the perl-lib path
on your system (eg. /usr/lib/perl5/5.6.8)

Copy the content of the etc directory to your system config files directory (eg.
/etc/archivista)

Now test the installation by executing the archivista.pl script


o Configuration
---------------

Edit the Archivista::Config.pm Package and configure the values for your system.

Create the global archivista database (archivista) with session and languages
table (dump file under /etc/archivista/dump/*). 
Default name for this global archivista database is 'archivista'. You can change
it and set the new name on Archivista::Config.pm
